  "detailed_description": "<strong>Realistic Store Management</strong><br> Design, customize, and manage every aspect of your store layout, ensuring a seamless shopping experience for your customers. Build various shelves. Fill them with different goods and clean them if products are spoiled.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032530/extras/1b5a237462d5f03fb96303e3ab492a56.poster.avif?t=1724774141\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032530/extras/1b5a237462d5f03fb96303e3ab492a56.webm?t=1724774141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032530/extras/1b5a237462d5f03fb96303e3ab492a56.mp4?t=1724774141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Fill market shelves</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032530/extras/98473e2d2335225ceab2e385f976c7e5.poster.avif?t=1724774141\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032530/extras/98473e2d2335225ceab2e385f976c7e5.webm?t=1724774141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032530/extras/98473e2d2335225ceab2e385f976c7e5.mp4?t=1724774141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Serve and Level Up</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032530/extras/6f604388ac104e602d8a68d466ad6faa.poster.avif?t=1724774141\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032530/extras/6f604388ac104e602d8a68d466ad6faa.webm?t=1724774141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032530/extras/6f604388ac104e602d8a68d466ad6faa.mp4?t=1724774141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Dynamic Economy</strong><br> Adapt to changing market trends, manage supply and demand, and adjust prices to maximize profits.<br><br><strong>Diverse Products</strong><br> Stock a wide variety of items, from fresh produce and dairy to household goods and specialty products.<br><br><strong>Customer Interactions</strong><br> Handle customer requests and complaints, manage checkout lines, and ensure high levels of customer satisfaction to build a loyal clientele.<br><br><strong>Expansion and Upgrades</strong><br> Expand your store space, unlock new features, and upgrade equipment to improve efficiency and attract more customers.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032530/extras/ee196548666cbe0a1bb9fdb5a099f5cf.poster.avif?t=1724774141\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032530/extras/ee196548666cbe0a1bb9fdb5a099f5cf.webm?t=1724774141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032530/extras/ee196548666cbe0a1bb9fdb5a099f5cf.mp4?t=1724774141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Seasonal Events</strong><br> Adapt to different events that can happen in world. From Bad Weather to Festivals.",
